g.text: Instigator's Tent: The plain red tent stands by dispassionately.

Instigator's Tent: Assorted softcovers, mostly pulp horror. A motor carriage lies buried in the snow on one cover, on another -- a ghost airship. You also see a collection of radio enthusiast magazines.
Savoir Faire: It was pitched by practised hands -- she's used to camping out.
Instigator's Tent: You pocket the worn brown leather journal.
Instigator's Tent: There she lies, cocooned in the sleeping bag, surrounded by empty cigarette packs, books, and half-read magazines.
Instigator's Tent: The instigator's body has been removed by Processing. The tent seems orphaned now.
Inland Empire: She watches by, motionless.
Kim Kitsuragi: "We should put her in the sleeping bag so the rats don't get to her."
Jump to: [Instigator's Tent: "The plain red tent rests stoically..."]
Instigator's Tent: The tent looks old but well-maintained. In the darkness of the tent -- a rolled-up sleeping bag, cooking utensils, some books and a kerosene lamp.
Inland Empire: A trusted friend left behind...
Instigator's Tent: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner.
Shine your flashlight on the books.
You: "Okay, let's carry her over here."
Logic: Magazines? You should look through them.
Kim Kitsuragi: "We should read this *immediately*. Like -- right now."
Instigator's Tent: You see a rolled-up sleeping bag and personal belongings.
Kim Kitsuragi: "See anything?" The lieutenant peeks in over your shoulder.
Savoir Faire: It was pitched by practised hands -- she was used to camping out.
Esprit de Corps: You'll need the lieutenant's help to carry her over.
Instigator's Tent: 'Rega Monthly', 'Journal of Material Science'. More technological digest. One of the magazines doesn't have images on the cover -- it's not a magazine, it's a leather notebook!
You: Back out of the tent.
Kim Kitsuragi: "I see the processing guys have been faster than usual. It's good we stopped by to check regardless." He nods at the lack of Ruby in the tent, then looks around. "Now -- island time."
Instigator's Tent: In the darkness of the tent: Ruby's body, zipped up in her sleeping bag. Next to the body -- some books and a kerosene lamp.
You: Sift through the books and magazines.
Shine your flashlight on the books and magazines.
Jump to: [Instigator's Tent: "Assorted softcovers, mostly pulp ho..."]
Instigator's Tent: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner. Ruby's dead body is wrapped in her sleeping bag.
Instigator's Tent: The plain red tent rests stoically in the corner.
